<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,152,1826]" pageId="7" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,304,699,725]" pageId="7" pageNumber="13">Habitat:</emphasis>
––This palm grows in primary forest in mixed Dipterocarp forest. Other palms that occupy the same habitat are 
<taxonomicName authority="(J. Dransf.) Dransfield (1984: 13)" authorityName="Dransfield" authorityPageNumber="13" authorityYear="1984" baseAuthorityName="J. Dransf." box="[348,1051,736,762]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Areca" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="7" pageNumber="13" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="insignis" variety="moorei">
<emphasis box="[348,516,737,762]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="13">Areca insignis</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[574,656,737,762]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="13">moorei</emphasis>
(J.Dransf.) 
